summary:
7+ years working with tech startups and scaleups in Boston, New York and the Netherlands. Working with a range of stakeholders including tech entrepreneurs, government players, regional stakeholders, venture capitalists and corporates.

üíöLaunched the Global Founder Network at Techleap.NL, a network of Dutch founders & operators abroad that pay-it-forward by helping out Dutch tech entrepreneurs willing to scale abroad faster and better
üåç At the Netherlands Consulate in New York, I liaised for the public private partnership Halve Maen to accelerate access of Dutch startups to the New York area.
‚ú® Interested in Health & Personal Development focused on systemic work, family constellations and enneagram types.
